research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"factorized_topk likely failed because its hidden mixer is too narrow and lossy; widening that stage and adding a gate should preserve more information before latent selection and materially improve FVU. Re-test factorized_topk at K=128 after this single architectural stabilization edit.","summary":"The first factorized_topk prototype was much worse than the anchor, but its implementation used a plain hidden layer with width equal to d_in, which is a likely bottleneck rather than a decisive family verdict. This round keeps the same family and K while upgrading the encoder to a wider gated mixer.","change_type":"edit_architecture","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This is a coherent follow-up on the only family that produced a strongly different signal, and it targets an obvious implementation bottleneck instead of abandoning the branch too early. The edit increases encoder compute, so even a quality gain still needs later cost scrutiny.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"8"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"}],"touched_files":["/root/sparsify-ascend/sparsify/factorized_topk_sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["The original factorized_topk prototype likely suffered from an overly narrow d_in-sized hidden bottleneck rather than only a bad family prior.","Round 5 stabilizes factorized_topk by replacing the narrow ReLU mixer with a wider gated hidden stage before latent projection."],"next_hypotheses":["If the stabilized factorized_topk proxy improves substantially, consider promotion or a follow-up quality pass with optimizer tuning.","If the stabilized factorized_topk remains poor under normal runtime, deprioritize the current built-in families and move to a genuinely new encoder family rather than more local tuning."]}
